name: Astolfo (Fate Series)
description:
I am new to making LorAs so this LorA might not be the best but If I make a better one in the future, I will update it.

If you want to see my upcoming LorAs, be sure to follow my twitter! @AkioA_I

To summon Astolfo's Pink Outfit: Astolfo, long braid, white hair, purple eyes, short sleeves, hair bow, black bow, pleated skirt, pink hair, serafuku, white thighhighs, pink skirt, single braid, navel, skirt, long hair, sailor collar, hair intakes, streaked hair, 1boy, school uniform

To Summon Astolfo's Purple Outfit: Astolfo, black skirt, long braid, braid, purple eyes, hair between eyes, striped, collarbone, hooded jacket, hair bow, 1boy, shirt, open clothes, black bow, pink hair, miniskirt, single braid, jacket, long hair, long sleeves, black pantyhose, purple jacket, hair intakes, streaked hair, striped shirt,


You can remove any clothing and replace to anything you desire.

Best is 0.6-0.7 if you want to change outfits, only a recommendation.

Be sure to give me feedback on the LorA so I can improve!
